    "description": "Execute a state machine transition on a task. Lead can use: lead_intervention_complete (rescope and reopen for worker), lead_approve (approve implementation and merge), force_close (requires replacement_task_ids for decomposition OR reason for redundant/already-landed tasks), escalate.",
