    "description": "Append a prompt amendment to a specialist agent role's learned_prompt. The amendment is appended after existing content (never replacing it) and logged to learned_prompt_history. Only applicable to specialist roles (worker, reviewer, resolver base_role). Do NOT use on architect, lead, or planner roles.",
